      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. The power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical M-variable differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed suspension bushings to preserve its original kinematics. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, offering a pure, analog driving experience with a taut, communicative steering rack and a robust power band that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
