      "description": "This 2018 Luxury AWD SUV is a prime example of a well-maintained vehicle that balances performance with everyday utility. Finished in a sophisticated Midnight Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the forward hood consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the Cream leather interior has been treated regularly; while there is slight natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin remains free of odors, stains, or tears. All electronic features\u2014including the panoramic sunroof, heated steering wheel, and premium 12-speaker sound system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound, having received full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake pad replacement. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a smoke-free, single-owner vehicle that comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys, offering a reliable and polished driving experience for its next owner.",
